text: Samuel George Claflin (born 27 June 1986) is an English actor. He is known for his roles as Philip Swift in Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (2011) and as Finnick Odair in The Hunger Games movie series. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English stage actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from Norfolk Category:Actors from Suffolk Category:People from Ipswich Category:People from Norwich
